### HU-021 — Consultar atención abierta de una admisión (creada automáticamente)
GET {{base}}/by-admission/1
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### HU-025 — Registrar triage (nivel III — Urgente)
# {id} = ID de la atención (atencion.id) obtenida del GET anterior
PATCH {{base}}/3/triage
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "triageLevel": "III",
  "chiefComplaint": "Dolor abdominal agudo en fosa ilíaca derecha con irradiación, acompañado de náuseas y fiebre",
  "systolicPressure": 130,
  "diastolicPressure": 85,
  "heartRate": 98,
  "respiratoryRate": 18,
  "temperature": 38.2,
  "oxygenSaturation": 97,
  "weight": 72.5,
  "height": 1.68,
  "glucometry": null,
  "observations": "Signo de McBurney positivo"
}

###

### HU-025 — Registrar triage (nivel I — Resucitación)
PATCH {{base}}/1/triage
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "triageLevel": "I",
  "chiefComplaint": "Paciente en paro cardiorrespiratorio",
  "systolicPressure": 0,
  "diastolicPressure": 0,
  "heartRate": 0,
  "respiratoryRate": 0,
  "temperature": 35.8,
  "oxygenSaturation": 70,
  "weight": 80.0,
  "height": 1.75,
  "glucometry": null,
  "observations": "Se inicia RCP inmediatamente"
}

###

### HU-025 — Registrar triage (nivel V — No urgente)
PATCH {{base}}/2/triage
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "triageLevel": "V",
  "chiefComplaint": "Resfriado común de 3 días de evolución, sin complicaciones",
  "systolicPressure": 115,
  "diastolicPressure": 75,
  "heartRate": 72,
  "respiratoryRate": 16,
  "temperature": 37.1,
  "oxygenSaturation": 99,
  "weight": 65.0,
  "height": 1.62,
  "glucometry": null,
  "observations": null
}

###

### HU-026 — Reclasificar triage (empeora de III a II)
PATCH {{base}}/1/triage/reclassify
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "newTriageLevel": "II",
  "justification": "Paciente presenta deterioro clínico: hipotensión y taquicardia progresiva, sospecha de sepsis abdominal"
}

###

### HU-026 — Reclasificar triage (mejora de II a IV)
PATCH {{base}}/2/triage/reclassify
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "newTriageLevel": "IV",
  "justification": "Paciente estabilizado tras analgesia. Signos vitales normales, dolor controlado"
}

###

### HU-027 — Cola de urgencias de la sede
GET {{base}}/emergency-queue
Authorization: {{token}}

